{
	"nodes":[
		{"id":"title","type":"text","text":"# roleplay-test-v2 유저 시나리오 디버그 맵\n시나리오 -> 이벤트 발생 -> 동작 코드 -> 문제 시 확인 지점","x":60,"y":-180,"width":920,"height":120,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"legend","type":"text","text":"읽는 법\n1) 왼쪽 시나리오 선택\n2) 가운데 이벤트/코드 확인\n3) 오른쪽 '문제 시 확인' 순서대로 점검\n\n색상: 시나리오(6), 이벤트(2), 코드(4), 디버그(1), 링크(5)","x":1020,"y":-180,"width":620,"height":150,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"h-s","type":"text","text":"사용자 시나리오","x":60,"y":-10,"width":260,"height":70,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"h-e","type":"text","text":"언제 어떤 이벤트가 발생?","x":350,"y":-10,"width":340,"height":70,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"h-c","type":"text","text":"동작 코드 위치","x":720,"y":-10,"width":360,"height":70,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"h-d","type":"text","text":"문제 생기면 여기부터","x":1110,"y":-10,"width":460,"height":70,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"s1","type":"text","text":"시나리오 1\n유저가 말을 시작/끝한다","x":60,"y":90,"width":260,"height":100,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"e1","type":"text","text":"이벤트\n- speech_started\n- input_audio_transcription.completed","x":350,"y":90,"width":340,"height":110,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"c1","type":"text","text":"코드\n- controllers/realtime/realtime-turn-controller.ts:380\n- controllers/realtime/realtime-turn-controller.ts:455","x":720,"y":90,"width":360,"height":120,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"d1","type":"text","text":"점검\n1) speech_started 로그가 찍히는지\n2) USER 무시 로그(누락/저신호/중복) 여부\n3) slot_detection 재시도 루프 여부","x":1110,"y":90,"width":460,"height":130,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"s2","type":"text","text":"시나리오 2\nassistant 발화가 끝난다\n(힌트 흐름 핵심)","x":60,"y":250,"width":260,"height":120,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"e2","type":"text","text":"이벤트\n- response.done(purpose=fsm_reply)\n예: assistantText='주문 도와드릴게요' 수신 시\n-> autoHint / text_enrichment / model.done 진행","x":350,"y":250,"width":340,"height":140,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"c2","type":"text","text":"코드\n- controllers/realtime/realtime-turn-controller.ts:275\n- controllers/realtime/realtime-turn-controller.ts:301\n- controllers/realtime/realtime-turn-controller.ts:352","x":720,"y":250,"width":360,"height":150,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"d2","type":"text","text":"점검\n1) response.done status 로그 확인\n2) requestAutoHintIfNeeded 호출 여부\n3) text_enrichment 응답 지연/누락 여부","x":1110,"y":250,"width":460,"height":140,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"s3","type":"text","text":"시나리오 3\n수동 테스트 버튼을 누른다","x":60,"y":430,"width":260,"height":100,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"e3","type":"text","text":"이벤트\n- sendManualText\n- sendManualSilence(stage 1/2)\n- detect.silence 이벤트 전송","x":350,"y":430,"width":340,"height":120,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"c3","type":"text","text":"코드\n- hooks/use-roleplay-test-v2-manual-actions.ts:53\n- hooks/use-roleplay-test-v2-manual-actions.ts:105\n- hooks/use-roleplay-test-v2-manual-actions.ts:108","x":720,"y":430,"width":360,"height":140,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"d3","type":"text","text":"점검\n1) 버튼 클릭 후 idempotency key 생성 여부\n2) detect.silence 액션이 applyFsmActions로 반영되는지\n3) 상태(currentSlot/missingSlots) 변화 확인","x":1110,"y":430,"width":460,"height":150,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"s4","type":"text","text":"시나리오 4\n연결/해제/종료 확인","x":60,"y":610,"width":260,"height":100,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"e4","type":"text","text":"이벤트\n- issueToken -> connectRealtime\n- ontrack / dataChannel.onopen\n- ui.showEndConfirm -> ui.end_confirm","x":350,"y":610,"width":340,"height":120,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"c4","type":"text","text":"코드\n- hooks/use-roleplay-test-v2-realtime-session-lifecycle.ts:142\n- controllers/realtime/realtime-lifecycle-controller.ts:181,192,217\n- hooks/use-roleplay-test-v2-turn-ops.ts:192","x":720,"y":610,"width":360,"height":150,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"d4","type":"text","text":"점검\n1) getUserMedia 권한/실패 메시지\n2) ontrack 후 오디오 재생/재부착\n3) end confirm 이후 followUp.actions 재적용 여부","x":1110,"y":610,"width":460,"height":140,"color":"1"},
